<body>
    <h1>How to Retrieve a BitLocker Recovery Key from Microsoft Intune</h1>
    <h2>Step-by-Step Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Sign in to the <strong>Microsoft Endpoint Manager admin center</strong> at <a href="https://endpoint.microsoft.com" target="_blank">https://endpoint.microsoft.com</a>.</li>
        <li>In the left-hand navigation pane, select <strong>Devices</strong>.</li>
        <li>Choose <strong>All devices</strong> and locate the device for which you need the BitLocker recovery key.</li>
        <li>Click on the device name to open its details.</li>
        <li>In the device overview pane, select <strong>Recovery keys</strong>.</li>
        <li>The BitLocker recovery key will be displayed. You can copy it or export it as needed.</li>
    </ol>
